cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper discusses the hyper-parameter configuration and training of recurrent neural networks, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also proposes a low computational cost model, which suggests a possible connection to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper discusses the expected performance of the network, which could be related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper mentions the recurrent neural network as a dynamic system, which could be related to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
